    {
      "title": "*ka-<div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\"></div>",
      "html": "<p><i class=\"foreign notranslate\">*kā-</i>，原始印欧语根，意为“喜欢，渴望”。</p><p>它构成或构成以下单词： <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of caress \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/caress\">caress</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of charity \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/charity\">charity</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of cherish \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/cherish\">cherish</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of Kama Sutra \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/Kama%20Sutra\">Kama Sutra</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of whore \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/whore\">whore</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of whoredom \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/whoredom\">whoredom</a>。</p><p>它是假设的来源，/证据表明它的存在由以下单词提供支持：梵语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">Kama</i>，印度爱神之名， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">kamah</i> “爱，渴望”； 古波斯语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">kama</i> “渴望”； 拉丁语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">carus</i> “亲爱的”； 古爱尔兰语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">cara</i> “朋友”； 古英语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">hore</i> “妓女，娼妓”。</p>"
